                    "locales": {
                        "en": {
                            "text": "<p>I’m {{Mohammad Bagher Amini}}, a backend-first full-stack engineer with [[~5 years]] of professional experience. I work mainly with {{JavaScript/TypeScript}}, {{Node.js}}, {{React}} and {{Next.js (TS)}}.</p><p>On the backend, I design clean APIs and data models with {{MongoDB}}, {{MySQL}}, and {{PostgreSQL}}. I use {{Redis}} for caching/queues and ship services in {{Docker}} on {{Linux}}. Through freelancing I’ve delivered projects with {{PHP (Laravel, Yii2)}}, {{ASP.NET}}, {{Angular}}, {{Vue}}, and {{Python/Django}} — not my primary stack, but I’ve successfully completed multiple real-world modules, especially in PHP.</p><p>I’m also curious about {{AI}}: I’ve experimented with [[fine-tuning]] and customized an LLM for personal use. On the frontend, I’m comfortable with {{Tailwind}}, {{HTML/CSS}}, and building reliable UIs. I’ve built several complex {{CRM}} systems end-to-end.</p><p>I look forward to collaborating [[with you!]]</p>"
                        }
                    }
                }
